ai-patthana8.53:0.2_0: under the investigation of principles, illustrious and confusion,
ai-patthana8.53:1.1_0: Not corruption, nor is Dhamma for the corruption of defilements. ...
ai-patthana8.53:3.1_0: Not corruption, nor defilements, and three things are not due to the defilements.
ai-patthana8.53:3.1_1: This is the section in brief.
